caption:
✨ Your empties deserve better than the trash ✨Did you know? Most beauty packaging can’t be recycled curb side due to mixed materials. That’s why this Global Recycling Day, our social team dropped off their used ELEMIS faves @ultabeauty ’s @Pact_Collective bin.

It’s easy to give your empties a second life: Use it up. Rinse it out. Drop it off.

♻️ As a B Corp brand, we’re committed to protecting biodiversity, positively impacting the climate and empowering our people and communities for a better future. Who’s joining us in dropping off your empties this week?
